<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_actions.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_actions.tpl) -->
    <!--Content-Begin-->
    <article>
            <h1>Husk at motionere din HPFI-afbryder</h1>
      <summary>
        <p>
                      
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->

Stor kampagne skal få danskerne til at teste deres fejlstrømsafbryder to gange om året.
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->
                            </p>
      </summary>
      <div class="pull-right social-icons">
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://sik.dk/Global/Presse/Nyheder-indtil-2015/Pressemeddelelser-2010/Husk-at-motionere-din-HPFI-afbryder" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square facebook-brand"></i></a>
<a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https://sik.dk/Global/Presse/Nyheder-indtil-2015/Pressemeddelelser-2010/Husk-at-motionere-din-HPFI-afbryder" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square twitter-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://sik.dk/Global/Presse/Nyheder-indtil-2015/Pressemeddelelser-2010/Husk-at-motionere-din-HPFI-afbryder" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest-square pinterest-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://sik.dk/Global/Presse/Nyheder-indtil-2015/Pressemeddelelser-2010/Husk-at-motionere-din-HPFI-afbryder" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square linkedin-brand"></i></a>
<a href="mailto:?subject=Husk at motionere din HPFI-afbryder&body=https://sik.dk/Global/Presse/Nyheder-indtil-2015/Pressemeddelelser-2010/Husk-at-motionere-din-HPFI-afbryder" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o mail-brand"></i></a>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
</div>
      <br>
      <hr>
        
              
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Lige om lidt stiller vi urene om til vintertid. Og står det til Sikkerhedsstyrelsen, skal danskerne samtidig bruge to minutter på at teste deres HPFI/HFI-afbryder (i daglig tale kaldet fejlstrømsafbryder).</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Styrelsen har som mål, at alle danskere bliver opmærksomme på at få testet deres afbryder. Det er nemlig den, der sikrer, at strømmen slår fra, når der er risiko for at få elektrisk stød. Og den kan derfor være med til at redde liv og forhindre alvorlige el-brande. Ved at ”motionere” afbryderen minimerer man risikoen for, at den sætter sig fast.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Og det er faktisk ganske let: Motion for HPFI- og HFI-afbrydere består i al sin enkelthed i et tryk på prøveknappen, som ofte er mærket med et &quot;T&quot;.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>- Når det er så vigtigt at motionere afbryderen på prøveknappen, er det fordi, man ved et enkelt tryk &quot;smører&quot; afbryderen. Vi håber, at danskerne vil tage budskabet til sig og teste to gange årligt, siger Mette Cramon, kommunikationskonsulent i Sikkerhedsstyrelsen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Sikkerhedsstyrelsen er derfor i gang med en stor kampagne, der opfordrer danskerne til at motionere afbryderen ved overgangene fra sommertid og vintertid.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Kampagnen tilbyder blandt andet en sms-tjeneste, der husker borgerne på at teste afbryderen. Men også en kampagnevideo med forklaring på, hvordan man gør.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Man kan finde mere information i vores 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="../../../../Virksomhed/El-for-fagfolk/Vejledninger-om-elarbejde/HPFI-hjoerne-supplerende-besky" title="Link til HPFI-hjørne" target="_self">HPFI-hjørne</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Pressen er velkommen til at kontakte kommunikationskonsulent, Mette Cramon på 33 73 20 65 for yderligere information og eksempler fra kampagnen.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
      
      
